{"type": "article", "id": 14601, "title": "黑胶唱片随身听", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-08T06:59:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060003124mlfievn3sgSTkyc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自德国汉堡的设计公司 rocket and wink 发布了黑胶唱片随身听系列 ‘rawman 3000’。采用黄、蓝、红三种颜色，分别对应 12 寸、10 寸和 8 寸，小巧便利，可以随时带在身上。而唱片的正面露出彩虹形窗口，活泼鲜艳。目前还是一个概念。<a href=\"http://www.rocketandwink.com/work/4466773/rawman_3000_portable_vinyl_players\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142056EjG3cfH6AqTz5KbI.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"818\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142056HwrcpfCmniLGJlkS.gif\" width=\"818\" height=\"524\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6405868\" data-format=\"gif\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142057zmb20EkP8vphgCsa.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"731\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.89364303\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142058BDAYSt2TqxLbvC41.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"732\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.89486553\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142058XwBEIGpj9Zg5Jcmz.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"750\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}